                    <p>Hyundai has packed the Creta EV with premium features such as ventilated seats, a panoramic sunroof, and a larger touchscreen. The Maruti e-Vitara, while more affordable, offers practical features like dual-zone climate control and connected car technology. Both vehicles ensure spacious cabins and top-notch safety features.</p>

