                    </ul>

                    <h5 class="subheading">2.	You need a longer range: </h5>
                    <ul>
                        <li>The ~450 km range gives it an edge for long-distance travel, reducing the need for frequent charging on road trips.</li>
    
                    </ul>

                    <h5 class="subheading">3.	You want a premium, tech-rich experience: </h5>
